269
00:24:17.455 --> 00:24:21.543
Mm. yum. You hungry?

270
00:24:31.303 --> 00:24:33.638
Yeah.
That's what I was afraid of.

271
00:24:34.347 --> 00:24:36.016
Oh. well. I... I mean.
I guess I should say

272
