280
00:25:02.500 --> 00:25:04.628
Trust me. I've seen a lot of TV.

281
00:25:06.296 --> 00:25:10.091
Well. um. you take care. buddy.

282
00:25:12.928 --> 00:25:13.678
Hmm.

283
00:25:13.762 --> 00:25:14.762
(CAMERA BEEPS)

284
00:25:15.931 --> 00:25:19.392
