1148
01:23:13.738 --> 01:23:15.448
The most painful way
to kill 'em.

1149
01:23:18.410 --> 01:23:20.453
And if I don't agree?

1150
01:23:21.329 --> 01:23:23.456
JONATHAN: I will have your
clinically depressed mother

1151
01:23:23.540 --> 01:23:25.542
