1195
01:27:19.776 --> 01:27:23.071
(GRUNTS)

1196
01:27:23.154 --> 01:27:27.158
(♪♪♪)

1197
01:27:34.248 --> 01:27:35.291
Okay.

1198
01:27:36.042 --> 01:27:38.127
