1200
01:27:41.673 --> 01:27:42.715
Oh. come on.

1201
01:27:42.799 --> 01:27:44.175
Come on. Where are you?

1202
01:27:44.259 --> 01:27:47.470
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

1203
01:28:12.161 --> 01:28:15.707
Oh. God.
I hope you can still hear me.

1204
01:28:18.334 --> 01:28:21.170
(SCREAMS)

1205
