1213
01:28:48.364 --> 01:28:50.575
(INDISTINCT YELLING)

1214
01:28:53.286 --> 01:28:57.206
(CROAK GROWLING)

1215
01:28:57.290 --> 01:28:59.250
(GROANING)

1216
01:29:00.585 --> 01:29:01.961
(SCREAMS)

1217
