1247
01:32:37.677 --> 01:32:39.387
Come on. Come on.

1248
01:32:41.097 --> 01:32:42.640
Renee. look out!

1249
01:32:42.723 --> 01:32:44.600
RENEE: Oh. my God! Go. go. go!

1250
01:32:46.727 --> 01:32:48.145
